                                        <div class=3D"faq-item-bottom">
                                            <p>The Gateway fails to start a=
nd logs the specific reference that couldn't be resolved. This fail-fast be=
havior is intentional: a Gateway running with missing credentials would fai=
l silently on the first API call, which is harder to debug than a startup e=
rror. Fix the secret reference, then restart.</p>

